              <tr>
                <td width="614" valign="top"><p><span class="style3"><em>Presentation &lsquo;IADC Global HSE safety case    template&rsquo; &ndash; Dominic Cattini</em> <em>&amp; Alan Spackman, IADC</em></span><br />
